column5: I fell asleep really early last night, which resulted in waking up at 5am... what better time to go fishin'. Weather wasn't too bad, I dipped as it got worse. As soon as I pulled up to my spot, my car hit 100,000kms... not bad for a 10 year old car. I caught a couple browns, only snapped a photo of the nicest one. Nice fight on an ultra light.
Ah, I was thinking of down the same until I saw the forecast, now I wish I had just done it! Nice little brown there!

Ah, I was thinking of down the same until I saw the forecast, now I wish I had just done it! Nice little brown there!  Yup. Went to work to catch up on some back logging. Should of went fishing too.LOL
hahaha, now i've got a bunch of housekeeping to do... but procrastination is strong in me today.
We logged 5 hours on the water without a sniff. Nobody else at the ramp had any better luck.
